ed (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode","title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode/Equatable-Implementations":{"abstract":[],"title":"Equatable Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode\/equatable-implementations","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/Equatable-Implementations","kind":"article","type":"topic"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/title","value":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/fragments","value":[{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/navigatorTitle","value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode"}],"op":"replace"}]}]}